    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><strong>Doing embedded development and research – reflections on the start of the Results4TB programme </strong></p>
<p><em>Sophie Witter, Professor of International Health Financing and Health Systems at Queen Margaret University, Edinburgh, shares her reflections on the gains and pains of the first 18 months of the Results4TB programme in Georgia.</em></p>]]></Value>
